2. Now main problem was that due to linux OS on my Jenkins server, there were permission problem for few of my node_modules folders , so build was getting failure every time.
So In my script section for Jenkins , I changed all directories permission for Jenkins workspace like 

       

&gt; chmod 777 &quot;Jenkins_nodeModules_path&quot;

3. then I added 

&gt; &quot;sudo npm install&quot;

 to same script.

So these changes were made on Jenkins project configuration to build project successfully.Hope it helps someone :-)

