---------------------------------

    Time consumption: 
    * START [Double precision test]...
    * STOP [Double precision test]:5.21951 s
    
    * START [CGAL simple]...
    * STOP [CGAL simple]:4.98616 s
    
    * START [CGAL GMPQ]...
    * STOP [CGAL GMPQ]:4.93984 s
    
    Factors:
      CgalSimple / Double = 0.955293
      CgalGmpq / Double = 0.946417

